    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The fruit of trees in the Malus genus. Domestic apples are usually green, red, or yellow, cultivated in temperate zones worldwide in a multitude of varieties.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
